evice_properties\" title=\"C\u00e1ch 3 : Disable dgpu b\u1eb1ng device properties\">C\u00e1ch 3 : Disable dgpu b\u1eb1ng device properties<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p>Ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0y d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c m\u00e1y c\u00f3 card r\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 khi fix sleep b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i disable card r\u1eddi \u0111i ( nh\u1eefng d\u00f2ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 )<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cach_1_Sua_config\"><\/span><strong><em>C\u00e1ch 1: S\u1eeda config\u00a0\u00a0<\/em><\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Openore\"><\/span>Openore<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>B1: Th\u00eam \u0111o\u1ea1n code sau v\u00e0o boot-arg \u201c-wegnoegpu\u201d\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B2: T\u1ea3i <a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/acidanthera\/gfxutil\/releases\">gfxutil<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B3: G\u00f5 l\u1ec7nh sau v\u00e0o terminal\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>K\u00e9o gfxutil v\u00e0o terminal nh\u1eadn code sau -f GFX0 ( nh\u01b0 h\u00ecnh )<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"602\" height=\"427\" src=\"https:\/\/lh5.googleusercontent.com\/6tUCYgfFlIzsP2sR0ET-S0Fxv49LVbta9wpXpmOVx-GoxJ5bEzC0K7cU0rSstmWZz10oK15y8sYkLXcf99SblF9JljCOBspbi2yWx4YQ6z3K59HLgDq-MG-gtNqRUo1ZbEuXDEeQ=s0\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>(do \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 card r\u1eddi | nh\u01b0ng vd gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb dup ra s\u1ebd l\u00e0 DevicePath = PciRoot(0x0)\/Pci(0x1,0x0)\/Pci(0x0,0x0)\/Pci(0x0,0x0)\/Pci(0x0,0x0))<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B3: Th\u00eam d\u00f2ng v\u1eeba dum v\u00e0o config nh\u01b0 sau\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>PciRoot(0x0)\/Pci(0x1,0x0)\/Pci(0x0,0x0)\/Pci(0x0,0x0)\/Pci(0x0,0x0) | dictionary&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B4: Th\u00eam c\u00e1c d\u00f2ng sau d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u00f2ng v\u1eeba add\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td>Name&nbsp;<\/td><td>data<\/td><td>2364697